		<div class="firstParagraph">
			<div>
				<h2>
					At the moment I live in Brazil but I'm from Argentina. I have been developing software for 4 years. My best experiences were in Santander Tecnolog√≠a and ITR resources as a Software engineer.
				</h2>
			</div>
		
		</div>
		<div class="article">
		<article>
			<p>
				There, I could put my knowledge into practice, for example, mobile development, web development. I acquired new skills like agile methodologies, daily workflow as well.
